Notebook[{

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["Amy\[CloseCurlyQuote]s Guide to Mathematics - from basics to the \
stars!", "Title",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8284531410191593`*^9, 
  3.828453155416018*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"957e397c-b6ba-43f6-9ba7-\
9c4f13e6a64a"],

Cell["Part One", "Chapter",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.828454043459392*^9, 
  3.82845406749181*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3fae3980-0c9a-4a66-9730-\
8efbd47d2a0e"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Section One: Bottom of the Barrel Basic Maths", "Chapter",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.828454069323709*^9, 
  3.8284540859766483`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7383ba9c-4d98-4d0b-ac4a-\
c0bd494bbb9c"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
These notes are taken from GCSE Mathematics Complete Revision and Practise \
Book by CGP\
\>", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.828454603356533*^9, 
  3.828454640901225*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"5ca15b5a-cdde-4ce3-bb8a-\
65c657a6a9f9"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["BODMAS", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.828453161932433*^9, 
  3.8284531715303802`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"01974e67-5097-463c-b6d0-\
d95be80a97f2"],

Cell["\<\
We' re going to start off by looking at how BODMAS can help us deal with \
operations in an equation . BODMAD tells us the order in which to tackle \
these operations. B = Brackets, O = Other (like squares), D = Division, M = \
Multiplication, A = Addition, S = Subtraction. 
EXAMPLE 1
Let\[CloseCurlyQuote]s try it out! If f = 4, g = 3 and h = -2, what is the \
answer to the following equation?\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.828453178527368*^9, 3.828453331043599*^9}, {
  3.8284542465068808`*^9, 
  3.828454265795266*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"df5db92c-49e6-46d3-821f-\
979593f2ed4c"],

Cell[BoxData[
 StyleBox[
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"e", " ", "=", " ", Cell[BoxData[
     FormBox[
      RowBox[{
       SuperscriptBox[
        RowBox[{"(", 
         RowBox[{"f", " ", "-", " ", "7"}], ")"}], "2"], "+", " ", 
       FractionBox[
        RowBox[{"4", "g"}], 
        RowBox[{"h", " ", "+", " ", "1"}]]}], TraditionalForm]], "Input",
     ExpressionUUID->"2b06a2dc-570b-48f8-a722-9d7080844b90"]}], ";"}], 
  "Input"]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.828451151263712*^9, 3.828451581768869*^9}, {
  3.828451626957559*^9, 3.828451659968171*^9}, {3.8284518440334463`*^9, 
  3.828451844785808*^9}, {3.828453295338887*^9, 3.828453300305808*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[11]:=",ExpressionUUID->"4ea8072d-30d0-444f-93d4-ba3eebc22eba"],

Cell["Let\[CloseCurlyQuote]s replace the letters with the numbers we know \
so...", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.828453335983666*^9, 3.828453345241878*^9}, {
  3.8284533927754383`*^9, 3.828453399899156*^9}, {3.828453432971541*^9, 
  3.828453469452999*^9}, {3.828453556714493*^9, 3.828453573731567*^9}, {
  3.828453699433476*^9, 3.828453707645698*^9}, {3.828453750791739*^9, 
  3.8284537744610147`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b663f251-f2c0-40d2-998e-\
e693b7c02845"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"e", " ", "=", " ", 
   RowBox[{
    SuperscriptBox[
     RowBox[{"(", 
      RowBox[{"4", " ", "-", " ", "7"}], ")"}], "2"], "+", " ", 
    FractionBox[
     RowBox[{"4", "*", "3"}], 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"-", "2"}], " ", "+", " ", "1"}]]}]}], ";"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.828453782569625*^9, 3.828453845053947*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[14]:=",ExpressionUUID->"6b01a229-b532-45bb-88e3-7f8c418c2439"],

Cell["\<\
So, let' s try and solve it in our head . Deal with the brackets first, which \
is (4-7) = -3. Then other which in this case is the square so -3^2 = 9. Then \
we deal with division, but to divide we need to know the numerator and \
denominator. Remember, around the top and bottom of a fraction are \
\[OpenCurlyQuote]invisible\[CloseCurlyQuote] brackets, so we need to work out \
the top and bottom before we continue. So 4*3 = 12 and -2 + 1 = -1 so 12/-1 = \
-12 so we have 9 + -12 = -3. Let\[CloseCurlyQuote]s enter e and see if we got \
the right answer! \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.828453852265834*^9, 3.828454007762129*^9}, {
  3.828454135256462*^9, 
  3.828454181776121*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b26e2717-09ca-438c-a0e9-\
4269ea410319"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData["e"], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.828454010147883*^9},
 CellLabel->"In[15]:=",ExpressionUUID->"2c9ae128-eb9c-4474-b8f8-7f203da1d4f8"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"-", "3"}]], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.828454011559926*^9},
 CellLabel->"Out[15]=",ExpressionUUID->"beb72b18-2299-49fe-81f3-30507db5617c"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
Hey! Amazing! Using BODMAS we got the right answer.
EXAMPLE 2
If a motorbike is brought for \[Sterling]6300 and depreciates in value by 45% \
over 3 years, how much is it worth at the end of three years? We know that \
100% of the bike\[CloseCurlyQuote]s worth = 6300. We want to work out 55%. So \
if we divide each side by 100 then times each side by 55, \
we\[CloseCurlyQuote]ll get the current value of the bike on the right hand \
side of the equation. Let\[CloseCurlyQuote]s try it!\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.828454015451447*^9, 3.828454026841227*^9}, {
  3.8284542684944677`*^9, 
  3.8284544032069893`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"360e2b99-fbe4-421b-a1c0-\
be1f57f1c0e1"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"b", " ", "=", " ", "6300"}], ";"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.828454406303266*^9, 3.8284544101879597`*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[16]:=",ExpressionUUID->"c9489883-3894-4fcc-bb77-c10bd0db0a5b"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"b", "/", "100"}], "*", "55"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8284544215774517`*^9, 3.828454425045814*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[17]:=",ExpressionUUID->"cfd6d1f5-05b5-4f7d-acb5-e12caabbb74c"],

Cell[BoxData["3465"], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.828454426382728*^9},
 CellLabel->"Out[17]=",ExpressionUUID->"588c9336-cebe-45cc-ad65-6809fbf3c69e"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
Yes, that' s the correct answer! We can also multiply the starting value by \
0.45 to get 45% of the value, then subtract this from the original value.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8284544363920097`*^9, 
  3.828454494099163*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"24bfdd4d-8049-4b7b-8709-\
5c36e5b2cef7"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"reduction", " ", "=", " ", 
   RowBox[{"b", " ", "*", " ", "0.45"}]}], ";"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.828454497890383*^9, 3.828454510894516*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[18]:=",ExpressionUUID->"72740fd7-8fef-45b3-871c-f56a1bf15530"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"b", " ", "-", " ", "reduction"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.828454514181027*^9, 3.828454516649795*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[19]:=",ExpressionUUID->"ed16ee78-61b5-493b-a432-6dd3f4fe6ec5"],

Cell[BoxData["3465.`"], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.828454518173572*^9},
 CellLabel->"Out[19]=",ExpressionUUID->"bf079492-e1b4-4de2-9a69-b56521d08a04"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["We get the same answer!", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.828454521177926*^9, 
  3.828454527282596*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a8c3609d-5532-4635-b94f-\
ef249f8eee31"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

